# Introduction

I wanted to write this book but I don't know why. I don't really have time and I
keep going over things in my mind that are out of my control.
It was covid-19.  I was working from home and everyday I woke up doomscrolling through
the same list of websites -
CNN, Huffpost, commafeed, ldsblogs, facebook, instagram, twitter, but I needed
something more - something to take my mind off of the impending election, my job.

So here it is.  I will try and 
